/* Table: "BC_BoothChangeApprove" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_BoothChangeApprove"
(
"ApproveID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32),
"ApproveFlowCode" VARCHAR(50),
"ApproveType" INTEGER,
"ApproveStatus" INTEGER,
constraint PK_BC_BOOTHCHANGEAPPROVE primary key ("ApproveID")
);

comment on table "BC_BoothChangeApprove" is

comment on column "BC_BoothChangeApprove"."ApproveType" is
'异动方案审批，主数据审批';

references "BC_BoothChange" (BCID);
